				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For other uses, see <a href="Islam_(disambiguation)" title="Islam (disambiguation)">Islam (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
<div class="metadata topicon nopopups" id="protected-icon" style="display:none; right:55px;"><a href="Wikipedia_Protection_policy#semi" title="This article is semi-protected."><img alt="Page semi-protected" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Padlock-silver.svg/20px-Padlock-silver.svg.png" width="20" height="20" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Padlock-silver.svg/30px-Padlock-silver.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Padlock-silver.svg/40px-Padlock-silver.svg.png 2x" /></a></div>
<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:222px;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Kaaba_at_night.jpg" class="image"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/Kaaba_at_night.jpg/220px-Kaaba_at_night.jpg" width="220" height="165" class="thumbimage" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/Kaaba_at_night.jpg/330px-Kaaba_at_night.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/10/Kaaba_at_night.jpg/440px-Kaaba_at_night.jpg 2x" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Kaaba_at_night.jpg" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/static-1.21wmf9/skins/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
The <a href="Kaaba" title="Kaaba">Kaaba</a>, in <a href="Mecca" title="Mecca">Mecca</a>, <a href="Saudi_Arabia" title="Saudi Arabia">Saudi Arabia</a>, is the <a href="Qibla" title="Qibla">center of Islam</a>. <a href="Muslim" title="Muslim">Muslims</a> from all over the world gather there to <a href="Prayer" title="Prayer">pray</a> in <a href="http://en.wiktionary.org/wiki/unity" class="extiw" title="wikt:unity">unity</a>.</div>
</div>
</div>
