<div class="NavHead" style="font-size:120%; color:#f7f1e3; background-color:#6bbbd4;"><a href="Prophets_in_Islam#Table_of_prophets.2Fmessengers_in_the_Quran" title="Prophets in Islam"><span style="color:#f7f1e3;">Prophets in the Quran</span></a></div>
