<b><a href="Riyadh_as-Saaliheen" title="Riyadh as-Saaliheen"><span style="color:#9e003a;">Rīaḍ As-Ṣāliḥīn</span></a></b> <i><span style="font-size:85%;">(1233–1278)</span></i> <b>-</b><br />
<b><a href="Mishkat_al-Masabih" title="Mishkat al-Masabih"><span style="color:#9e003a;">Mishkat Al-Masabih</span></a></b> <i><span style="font-size:85%;">(1340)</span></i> <b>-</b><br />
<b><a href="Talkhis_al-Mustadrak" title="Talkhis al-Mustadrak" class="mw-redirect"><span style="color:#9e003a;">Talkhis Al-Mustadrak</span></a></b> <i><span style="font-size:85%;">(1274–1348)</span></i> <b>-</b><br />
<b><a href="Majma_al-Zawa'id" title="Majma al-Zawa'id"><span style="color:#9e003a;">Majma Al-Zawa'id</span></a></b> <i><span style="font-size:85%;">(1335–1405)</span></i> <b>-</b><br />
